Manage Templated Apps

CRM Analytics templated apps have multistep processes for installation and upgrades. Use the App Install History page to monitor installations in progress, track assets created for the app, and view logs to troubleshoot any installation issues.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

From Setup, enter App Install History, and select App Install History.

Only Templated apps shared with manage access are visible to the user.

The home page shows installed CRM Analytics templated apps shared with manage access. Embedded apps that are auto-installed and templated apps installed from Analytics Studio are listed here.

App Refresh

When an app is installed, data assets used by the app must be refreshed to provide up-to-date insights. To refresh all of the data assets for an installed app, run a data refresh on-demand or create a schedule.

To run a data refresh immediately, select Refresh Now from the app's actions. To schedule regular data refreshes, select Schedule.

Click an app name to see install history, cancel running installations, and view app logs and state.
title: Managing Templated Apps in CRM Analytics
